text: Gabrielle Anwar (born 4 February 1970) is an English actress. She played Margaret Tudor on The Tudors. She also played "The Tango Girl" in Scent of a Woman. She later played Fiona in the television series Burn Notice. Anwar was born in Laleham, Surrey, England. ==References== Category:English television actors Category:English movie actors Category:1970 births Category:Living people
